    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/yayashiny/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u54353302-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yayashiny/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">飞猪</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-10-16"
      class="main-meta">2011-10-16 19:58:13</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5133455_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  并非评论，只是笔记。 张居正出生于明朝嘉靖年，奸臣严嵩当政时期。原名张白圭，在当地考生员时被当时主考官正式更名为张居正。 23岁进士出身，从此踏上仕途。从他进入朝堂到他当权，中间大部分是件，他都是韬光养晦。 徐阶斗走了严嵩，高拱又斗走了徐阶，最后张居正斗走了高拱...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5133455_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5133455_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





